<br>
IF IT AINT BROKE, DONT FIX IT.<br>
<br>
which simply put, means.  LEAVE MY STAFF ALONE.<br>
<br>
we couldnt ask for anything more UBER if you will.  Leave it just the way it is.<br>
<br>
We are all gripeing and complaining about class balance, some of the things i seen posted here, just throw that out the window, they would make wizards far to powerful.  Hell, as of now, a properly played wizard is more powerful than just about anyone else.<br>
<br>
Insta click epic rune = Wizards as main tanks.  Just stick it on a hot key and pound it for a while, the buff itself draws uber aggro if your in aggro range.  Casting it 50times a second = no damage taken = aggro constantly on you = no more need for warriors.<br>
<br>
Raising the damage it absorbs = over powerd.  As of now, im out tanking Tanks in Velks groups with the thing.  And i get told to sit on my butt, and stop trying to do the warriors job.  Though he takes more damage than i do.<br>
<br>
We all complain about how &quot;so and so got this kind of item, wheres ours.&quot;  Im sorry boys and girls, verant designed this game for the high end.  As long term subscribers play the high end, thats what they develop for the future.  And as far as High end items go, the Wizard Epic, as it sits is by far one of the most UBER, next to the cleric and possibly the rogue.<br>
<br>
The thing already has a FT3 effect on it,  it absorbs nearly twice the damage that a chanter rune can.  and its got 100 mana on it, and 25 intel.  Only mages have compareable intel and mana, and noone else has the FT3 effect.<br>
<br>
So why are we even discussing changeing something that is so Vital to our existance in the high end encounter.  I am of the opinion here, that if you dont have it... dont try and change it for those of us that do, and love it just the way it is.<br>
<br>
Anyone here have there epic and want it changed, please send me a tell, so i can drag you into the street, shoot you down, and hang your dead corpse from a tree as a symbol of what happens when wizards are stupid.<br>
<br>
